878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點界定話粒白波打唔到object ball？球證決定</blockquote><br />\n係,球證睇 如果難判定嘅話會直頭拎波擺喺object ball左右兩邊咁睇"},{"pid":"5d41dc3815fa9ca7a3a022bf7a5d5884a97794b5","tid":336763,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"想學打<br />\n一條友去鳩打怕比人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d37c69d70df00d6177fd11e81aa415d12eea72","tid":336763,"uid":37878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下唔同情況kissing 點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩係知如果到我打紅波但kiss 左紅波 就可以就咁打去邊都得</blockquote><br />\n係 如果係touch紅波但係要打黑波嘅話,只要紅波冇郁到都冇foul"},{"pid":"c3867b2ab4322ebf1a9fada819f369cbc9344350","tid":336763,"uid":118677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下唔同情況kissing 點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩係知如果到我打紅波但kiss 左紅波 就可以就咁打去邊都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncolor ball 一樣"},{"pid":"20ad778d61f81bac74b2bcc0f24f0522d21ffaf7","tid":336763,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"如果對手打唔到obj ball 係咪可以無限要求佢重打博佢狂扣分（定係我狂加分）or仲有咩選擇"},{"pid":"cd2825bcb1f07e8d95a4b7bbb69cc4ccda740934","tid":336763,"uid":119591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"想問下邊到有桌球新手班<br />\n打左幾年想重新學過姿勢同企位"},{"pid":"6b64b75948002f09084bfd09c0a26fe3bc4c018d","tid":336763,"uid":100099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"初哥留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ffeca05c65cfdd428f8e2db899c31a4abb18a7","tid":336763,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初哥留名<img 