到嘅話,球證都可以剩係call foul<br />\n不過唔係咁多球證敢call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過可能都唔想濫用啩,始終好似變相懲罰safety打得好嘅球手</blockquote><br />\n原來有分淨係foul 同埋foul and miss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問有咩分別</blockquote><br />\nFoul是咪扣分 miss就加對手分"},{"pid":"28419d39289315c7784f4e5e6189201bb8f8ed9d","tid":336763,"uid":118562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果對手打唔到obj ball 係咪可以無限要求佢重打博佢狂扣分（定係我狂加分）or仲有咩選擇</blockquote><br />\n係你狂加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加到你超分就得foul冇miss,唔可以重擺<br />\n如果佢留低機會你咪可以揀自己打</blockquote><br />\n好似唔使超分,但球證覺得你已經盡左力救都會剩係foul無miss?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 有啲好難救嘅波而你差少少就救到嘅話,球證都可以剩係call foul<br />\n不過唔係咁多球證敢call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過可能都唔想濫用啩,始終好似變相懲罰safety打得好嘅球手</blockquote><br />\n原來有分淨係foul 同埋foul and miss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問有咩分別</blockquote><br />\nFoul是咪扣分 miss就加對手分</blockquote><br />\n桌球只有加分無扣分,foul&amp;miss係對手可以要求重擺要你再救過,foul就唔得"},{"pid":"21bf0565a0c38995452706e6fb6e8c54fe528f96","tid":336763,"uid":32403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新手想問下啲規則<br />\n點解對手打唔到白波 之後你可以連續打2粒color波既？</blockquote><br />\n你講嘅情況應該係free ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係對手打唔到object ball,而個白波位置唔能夠打到object ball左右一個波位,咁就有free ball<br />\n你可以打一個colour當紅波,之後再打colour</blockquote><br />\n有例外case 之前637講過</blockquote><br />\n桌球例仲係太多灰色地帶<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔係steve davis呢D老前輩無野做 無聊去逐條球例睇都唔會有人知<br />\n<br />\n所以都係講返基本大家知既就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b004b082c19beb8c27